<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white font-sans text-gray-800">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 py-12 border-b border-gray-100">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight"
        >
          Packaging & Delivery
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
          From our farms to your doorstep, we ensure every fruit is handled with
          care, packed securely, and delivered fresh.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="py-20 px-20">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <span
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#E8F5E9] text-[#2E7D32] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl"
                >01</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                Rigorous Quality Check
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Before packaging, every batch undergoes a strict inspection. We
              manually check for freshness, size, and health. As seen in our
              process, we inspect items like corn and bananas individually to
              ensure only the best produce makes it to the box.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="ph-fill ph-check-circle text-[#4CAF50]"></i>
                Hand-picked selection
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="ph-fill ph-check-circle text-[#4CAF50]"></i> Freshness
                verification
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <span
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFEBEE] text-[#D32F2F] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl"
                >02</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                Precision Weighing
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Honesty is our policy. We use calibrated digital scales to ensure
              you get exactly what you paid for. Whether it's a bulk order of
              watermelons or crates of bananas, our weighing process is
              transparent and accurate.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <span
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#E8F5E9] text-[#2E7D32] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl"
                >03</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                Protective Packaging
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              We use high-grade corrugated boxes and protective liners to
              prevent damage during transit. Our "Shorya 121" and other premium
              banana brands are packed systematically to maintain airflow and
              prevent bruising.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12">
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <span
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFEBEE] text-[#D32F2F] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl"
                >04</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                Loading & Dispatch
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Our logistics team ensures that goods are loaded efficiently to
              maximize stability. We work with trusted transport partners to
              deliver bulk wholesale orders across India promptly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">On-Site Gallery</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div
            class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:opacity-90 transition"
          >
            <img
              src="images/delivery/packing.png"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:opacity-90 transition"
          >
            <img
              src="images/delivery/qulityCheck.png"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:opacity-90 transition"
          >
            <img
              src="images/delivery/weightCheck.jpeg"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:opacity-90 transition"
          >
            <img
              src="images/delivery/image.png"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#2E7D32] py-12 text-white">
      <div
        class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-center md:text-left gap-8"
      >
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Bulk Orders? No Problem.</h3>
          <p class="text-green-100">
            We have the capacity to handle large scale wholesale requirements.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="bg-white text-[#2E7D32] font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition"
        >
          Contact For Bulk Deal
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
